<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbfb9aa91-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s13286"><num value="13286">§ 13286.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary for purposes of this part $50,000,000 for the 10-year period beginning with the first full fiscal year after <date date="1992-10-24">October 24, 1992</date>, to remain available until expended.</p>
